    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "PowerShell itself doesn't have any options for this, but it also doesn't really have a way to surface it.  You can use win32 API's (or I think sysinternals might have a tool for it?) to set something up like this yourself, but if you'd like the feature baked into conhost/terminal you'd want to file the issue on [microsoft/terminal](https://github.com/microsoft/terminal) or feedback hub/user voice.",
